data.description: An incredible opportunity to own a beautiful single level home on a corner lot in one of Murrieta's newest communities. This 4 BDR 2 Bathroom home built in 2016 is surrounded by incredible parks, recreational areas, schools, shopping centers & restaurants! The sprawling one story layout is ample & spacious with a modern floorplan combining a large, open concept kitchen with an elongated granite counter top center island perfect for entertaining, with the living room and breakfast area. The crisp & bright white kitchen cabinets bring in tons of light & the abundant counter top space is perfect for your culinary ambitions & the dedicated pantry give you extra storage. With the 3 extra bedrooms on the opposite end of the primary bedroom, you can tuck the kiddos at night and enjoy some added privacy & separation for a good night's sleep. The primary has an elegantly remodeled bathroom with sleek grey tile flooring, a spacious walk in shower with glass doors & a rainfall style showerhead, as well as a walk in closet. Enjoy a low maintenance front & back yard with desert scaping & turf along with extra shade from the extended awning. Murrieta living at it's best with all the suburban amenities & comforts with no stairs to march up or down. The home is equipped with solar panels.
